userinterface.properties.computation

Class SimulateModelCheckThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • userinterface.GUIComputationThread
        • userinterface.properties.computation.SimulateModelCheckThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class SimulateModelCheckThread
extends GUIComputationThread
    Thread that executes approximate (simulation-based) model checking of a property via PRISM. Model should have been loaded into PRISM already. Supplied are: properties file (constants defined), list of properties to be (approximately) verified and initial state (default/random if null).
